---
title: Pork and Brussels Sprout Salad with Kale and Mustard Vinaigrette
description: Roasted Brussels and kale combine for one heck of a tasty salad! Beautiful pan-seared pork chops, pumpkin seeds and a simple mustard vinaigrette adorn this fall-inspired salad!

